Setup and Running Instructions
Install dependencies:

bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
Prepare your dataset:

Place audio files in data/raw/

Create train/val/test splits in data/splits/

Run training:


python scripts/train.py --config configs/base_config.yaml

Run inference:


python scripts/inference.py --config configs/base_config.yaml --model best_model.pth --input test.wav --output output.wav

This complete implementation provides all the necessary components for your voice-to-voice system, from data processing to model training and real-time inference.